    "description": "<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>欢迎来到《青蛙》，这是一款终极收集游戏，在这里您可以测试自己的点击、战斗和养殖技能！</strong></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >点击收集青蛙，加入洞穴战斗，提升等级并解锁新内容。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>点击青蛙：</strong> 以最快的速度点击屏幕上的青蛙。每次点击都会让您更接近解锁惊喜奖励。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061650/extras/f88cd6ab378619c9a25425789d0fc386.poster.avif?t=1765309496\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061650/extras/f88cd6ab378619c9a25425789d0fc386.webm?t=1765309496\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061650/extras/f88cd6ab378619c9a25425789d0fc386.mp4?t=1765309496\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>加入战斗：</strong>摧毁水晶，提升青蛙等级，打败老板，在困难模式中考验自己！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061650/extras/4f3409c1f308d8a9367527504c4ef134.poster.avif?t=1765309496\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061650/extras/4f3409c1f308d8a9367527504c4ef134.webm?t=1765309496\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061650/extras/4f3409c1f308d8a9367527504c4ef134.mp4?t=1765309496\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>解锁水晶：</strong> 每次点击都有机会获得特殊宝箱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061650/extras/8bd6708e623c00bfc469c8df63843f74.poster.avif?t=1765309496\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061650/extras/8bd6708e623c00bfc469c8df63843f74.webm?t=1765309496\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061650/extras/8bd6708e623c00bfc469c8df63843f74.mp4?t=1765309496\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>装备你的青蛙：</strong> 装备您收集的青蛙，每次点击都能提高您的得分，购买升级物品并扩大您的青蛙农场。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061650/extras/fc46d077d581bcc47afd1f257c23a4c3.poster.avif?t=1765309496\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061650/extras/fc46d077d581bcc47afd1f257c23a4c3.webm?t=1765309496\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061650/extras/fc46d077d581bcc47afd1f257c23a4c3.mp4?t=1765309496\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>您准备好成为终极青蛙收集者了吗？在《青蛙》中尽情发挥您的聪明才智，看看您能找到多少稀有青蛙！</strong></p></li></ul>",
